\
Both rivers originate in the western mountains and flow into the Krbsh Sea. The southern river, the 
\f2\i Setta
\f0\i0 , drains into the Great Lake of Bye, created by the formidable dams built by the inhabitants of Byenung.  Along with its natural course into the Krbsh Sea, now by way of the Lake of Bye, the 
\f2\i Setta
\f0\i0  also drains into and provides navigation to the Bay of Bar to the south. \
\
The navigable Great Bye Canal ties the Great Lake of Bye to the Bay of Bar.  Another navigable canal, the Bye-Nye Waterway, connects the Great Lake to the Arql Sea\
\
For now, most of the action in the story and the game takes place within the Lands of Saskantinon. \
