\f0\b0 \cf0 As they flow through the Ringtoons, the 
\f2\i Pavan
\f0\i0  and the 
\f2\i Setta
\f0\i0  mark both geographic and political divides. Only in the area around Lake of Bye do the same sub-regional language and cultural and economic norms appear on both banks of the 
\f2\i Setta
\f0\i0 .  As with the Ring Road, the two rivers serve as both boundary and transport; they provide a dividing-line as well as a common thread.  \
